{"type":"tool_execution_end","toolCallId":"call_a87a0aff5ebe452c860eee91","toolName":"mcp","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C2\ncase_id: arb-ex11a-20260630141638\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C2\nremaining_ms: 882215\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex11a-20260630141638\",\"member_id\":\"C2\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:24:59Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_25136676d648_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-25136676d648\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-25136676d648.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Corroborates that NOTAM OIIX A1010/26 announced closure of airports across the western Tehran FIR, with limited daylight operations and fresh CAA approval for passenger flights; describes non-weather military/diplomatic context.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T14:25:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"25136676d648360a3c4d2329f64e071677d51e8d2dc36aa30b7dbcf314121c79\",\"size_bytes\":1103,\"source_description\":\"Siasat.com webpage captured via web open; selected relevant page text and metadata from lines 23-34 and 39-65.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.siasat.com/trump-considers-new-iran-strikes-as-diplomacy-enters-critical-phase-3475705/\",\"storage_name\":\"25/25136676d648360a3c4d2329f64e071677d51e8d2dc36aa30b7dbcf314121c79\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Siasat report on NOTAM OIIX A1010/26, May 23 2026\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:27:26Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_5e5109b5ca63_submitted-evidence-03-defendant-5e5109b5ca63\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-defendant-5e5109b5ca63.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Shows the raw NOTAM wording available from a NOTAM aggregator. The text frames the measure as airport-operations closures in the west part of Tehran FIR, lists exceptions operating sunrise-to-sunset, requires new permission for civil IFR passenger flights, and shows A1015/26 replacing A1010/26 with a longer exception list before the deadline.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T14:28:30Z\",\"sha256\":\"5e5109b5ca632110b53c1e6f333fa92259a70d8b970b57de188d7b8dbcc1bce7\",\"size_bytes\":2376,\"source_description\":\"Notamify OIIX NOTAM pages retrieved via web open on 2026-06-30. Captured visible page metadata, interpretation, and raw NOTAM text for A1010/26 and replacement A1015/26.\",\"source_url\":\"https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/693f2d0f-54d3-433b-8128-49f5475ba269 and https://notamify.com/notams/OIIX/67435351-52f9-4d17-8f4c-497a21dd94bf\",\"storage_name\":\"5e/5e5109b5ca632110b53c1e6f333fa92259a70d8b970b57de188d7b8dbcc1bce7\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Notamify raw text for OIIX A1010/26 and replacement A1015/26\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:27:42Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_6057a17cc5bf_submitted-evidence-04-defendant-6057a17cc5bf\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-defendant-6057a17cc5bf.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Provides a contrary/source-chain complication: Iran's Civil Aviation Organization spokesperson reportedly denied a new official aviation notice imposing nationwide airspace restrictions and said flights were operating according to schedule, while the same report acknowledges an earlier western-Tehran-FIR airport activity suspension with exemptions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T14:28:45Z\",\"sha256\":\"6057a17cc5bf9d03bc6a13a3f87c381c3974e116d8d6e2a3a9ecd39961ab6e61\",\"size_bytes\":1142,\"source_description\":\"Iran International webpage retrieved via web open on 2026-06-30; captured article title, times