"relevance\":\"Provides a contrary/source-chain complication: Iran's Civil Aviation Organization spokesperson reportedly denied a new official aviation notice imposing nationwide airspace restrictions and said flights were operating according to schedule, while the same report acknowledges an earlier western-Tehran-FIR airport activity suspension with exemptions.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T14:28:45Z\",\"sha256\":\"6057a17cc5bf9d03bc6a13a3f87c381c3974e116d8d6e2a3a9ecd39961ab6e61\",\"size_bytes\":1142,\"source_description\":\"Iran International webpage retrieved via web open on 2026-06-30; captured article title, timestamp, and relevant lines 39-55.\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.iranintl.com/en/202605239595\",\"storage_name\":\"60/6057a17cc5bf9d03bc6a13a3f87c381c3974e116d8d6e2a3a9ecd39961ab6e61\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Iran International report: Iran denies new NOTAM limiting flights across country\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-30T14:24:42Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_6877e32e36e2_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-6877e32e36e2\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-6877e32e36e2.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Reports that Iran's Civil Aviation Authority issued NOTAM OIIX A1010/26 on May 22, valid until May 25, closing all airports in the western Tehran FIR and limiting remaining airports to daylight operations with fresh per-flight CAA approval.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-30T14:25:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"6877e32e36e2b58bf10a9b2d917614c815931dc94d707627c69bb1fc195f509c\",\"size_bytes\":1524,\"source_description\":\"The Indian Express webpage captured via web open; selected relevant page text and metadata from lines 20-61 and 100-115.\",\"source_url\":\"https://indianexpress.com/article/world/us-news/iran-closes-airspace-trump-cancels-plans-us-military-strikes-